---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Maine Cannabis Education & Training Resources" 
  description="Cannabis industry training programs, certifications, and educational resources for Maine entrepreneurs and employees. Metrc training, budtender certification, and business development courses."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-152陶?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <article class="resource-hub">
    <div class="hub-header">
      <h1>Maine Cannabis Education & Training</h1>
      <p class="lead">Curated educational resources for Maine cannabis entrepreneurs, employees, and aspiring operators. From seed-to-sale tracking certification to budtender training programs.</p>
    </div>

    <Callout title="For Business Founders" type="passion">
      Beyond licensing, building a compliant, profitable cannabis business requires ongoing education. Bookmark this page and check back quarterly — we update it as new programs launch in Maine.
    </Callout>

    <div class="resource-sections">

      <section class="resource-section" id="seed-to-sale">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">📊</span>
          <h2>Seed-to-Sale Tracking (Metrc)</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Maine requires all licensed cannabis businesses to use Metrc for inventory tracking from seed to sale. Certification and training are available through the following channels.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Metrc Official Training</h3>
            <p>Mandatory training for all Maine cannabis licensees using the Metrc tracking system.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.metrc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metrc Homepage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.metrc.com/training/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metrc Training Portal</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Metrc Requirements</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Metrc Implementation Partners</h3>
            <p>Third-party consultants who help businesses set up and optimize their Metrc integration.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.cannabisbusinesstimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cannabis Business Times — Metrc Guides</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-inventory-management/">Our Inventory Management Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="budtender">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🌿</span>
          <h2>Budtender & Staff Training</h2>
        </div>
        <p>While Maine doesn't mandate specific budtender certifications, reputable operators invest in trained staff for compliance and customer experience.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Responsible Vendor Training</h3>
            <p>Training programs for dispensary staff on compliance, customer service, and product knowledge.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/resources" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Responsible Vendor Guidance</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.leafly.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Leafly Learning — Budtender Resources</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Product Knowledge</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.cannabisbusinesstimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cannabis Business Times — Product Guides</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-edibles-compliance/">Our Edibles Compliance Guide →</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-delivery-rules/">Our Delivery Rules Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="business">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">📈</span>
          <h2>Business Development</h2>
        </div>
        <p>General business education programs that serve Maine entrepreneurs, including cannabis-specific resources.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine SBDC</h3>
            <p>Free business counseling and training for Maine entrepreneurs, including those in regulated industries like cannabis.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/decd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine DECD</a> — SBDC and small business resources</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>SCORE Maine</h3>
            <p>Free mentoring from experienced business professionals. SCORE mentors can advise on cannabis business planning.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://webwc03.score.org/maine" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SCORE Maine</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.score.org/mentors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find a Mentor</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Chamber of Commerce</h3>
            <p>Business networking, advocacy, and educational programming for Maine businesses.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.mainechamber.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Chamber Homepage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.mainebiz.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MaineBiz — Business News</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Cannabis Business Certifications</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.cannabisbusinesstimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cannabis Business Times Certification Guides</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://mjbizdaily.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MJBiz — Industry Events & Training</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="compliance">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">⚖️</span>
          <h2>Compliance & Regulatory Training</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Ongoing compliance education for Maine cannabis operators and their employees.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>OCP Stakeholder Engagements</h3>
            <p>Public hearings, listening sessions, and regulatory updates from Maine's Office of Cannabis Policy.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Homepage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/stakeholder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Stakeholder Sessions</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-regulations/">Our Regulations Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Security & Safety Training</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dps/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Dept. of Public Safety</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-security/">Our Security Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="cultivation">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🌱</span>
          <h2>Cultivation & Production Training</h2>
        </div>
        <p>For operators pursuing cultivation, manufacturing, or production licenses in Maine.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Growing Standards</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.cannabisbusinesstimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cannabis Business Times — Cultivation</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-cultivation-guide/">Our Cultivation Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Manufacturing & Extraction</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-extraction-licensing/">Our Extraction Licensing Guide →</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-edibles-compliance/">Our Edibles Compliance Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Testing & Quality</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-product-testing-guide/">Our Product Testing Guide →</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Testing Rules (Chapter 5)</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>

    <Callout title="Build Your Knowledge Foundation" type="info">
      Start with our free resources — then layer in paid certifications as your business grows. The best operators treat compliance education as an ongoing investment, not a one-time checkbox.
    </Callout>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .resource-hub { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  
  .hub-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .hub-header h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lead { font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
  
  .resource-sections { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  
  .resource-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .section-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
  .resource-section > p { color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  
  .resource-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .resource-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .resource-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .resource-card > p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  
  .resource-links { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .resource-links li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .resource-links a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .resource-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</Layout>
